sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor PublicHealth as "Public Health Official"
    participant WebPortal as "Web Portal"
    participant Analytics as "Analytics Engine"
    participant ML as "ML Model Service"
    participant Weather as "Meteorological Service (External)"
    participant CentralDB as "Central Database"

    Note over PublicHealth,CentralDB: FR14-FR17: Outbreak Prediction and Visualization
    PublicHealth->>WebPortal: Request risk map (region: Somali)
    WebPortal->>Analytics: GET /prediction/risk-map
    par Data aggregation
      Analytics->>CentralDB: Fetch health data (coverage, zero-dose)
      CentralDB-->>Analytics: Health dataset
      Analytics->>Weather: Fetch rainfall/temp (last 30 days)
      Weather-->>Analytics: Weather dataset
    end
    Analytics->>ML: Execute models (health + weather)
    rect rgb(255, 248, 180)
    ML->>ML: Run KNN (spatial clustering)
    ML->>ML: Run XGBoost (cholera prediction)
    alt Risk score > threshold
      ML->>ML: Tag "High Risk Zone"
    else No data reporting
      ML->>ML: Tag "Silent District"
    end
    end
    ML-->>Analytics: Return GeoJSON vectors
    Analytics-->>WebPortal: Risk map data
    WebPortal->>WebPortal: Render heatmap layer
    WebPortal-->>PublicHealth: Display interactive map
